                conversions.
            </p>

            <div class="max-w-lg mx-auto">
                <div
                    class="font-sans text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed pl-3 border-l-2 sm:border-l-3 border-blue-500 mb-6 md:mb-8 text-left"
                >
                    <p>
                        Our premium website development services are designed
                        specifically for SaaS companies and startups looking to
                        make an impact.
                    </p>
                    <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-medium text-blue-600">
